    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it honestly looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it strictly garage-kept and meticulously detailed. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust on it! If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' ride without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one. Come see it for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
