    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically impeccable, having undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with ARP bolts, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, transferring power through a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis dynamics are preserved with refreshed bushings and OEM Bilstein dampers. Finished in Titanium Silver over Imola Red Nappa leather, the finish exhibits zero oxidation and the interior retains its factory matte texture. A turn-key masterpiece for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
