      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show zero wear or bolster compression, and the original factory scent still lingers. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records meticulously organized and available for review. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, the attention to detail is evident in every corner. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence, perfect for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
